{"id":"2MM7H2NPN","name":"project_RL_nhom9","paragraphs":[{"user":"sin235","progress":0,"config":{"lineNumbers":true,"tableHide":false,"editorSetting":{"language":"plain_text","editOnDblClick":true,"completionKey":"TAB","completionSupport":false},"editorMode":"ace/mode/plain_text","colWidth":12,"fontSize":9,"editorHide":true,"results":{},"enabled":true},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"apps":[],"runtimeInfos":{},"progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"jobName":"paragraph_1774070988173_1360656053","id":"paragraph_1774070988173_1360656053","dateCreated":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:29:48 AM","status":"FINISHED","focus":false,"text":"%md\r\n# Demo Learning Progress Cho PPO Trading\r\n\r\nNotebook nay duoc doi huong de phuc vu demo voi thay: khong chi xem pipeline du lieu, ma con thay duoc thuat toan thay doi the nao tu luc moi hoc den luc hoc xong.\r\n\r\n## Flow de demo\r\n1. Paragraph setup dung `%spark.pyspark` de load du lieu processed va tao temp view `trading_features_demo`.\r\n2. Paragraph progress doc artifact trong `results/runs` va tinh 2 giai doan cho tung run:\r\n   `Early` = trung binh cum episode dau, `Late` = trung binh cum episode cuoi.\r\n3. Paragraph `%angular` tao giao dien tuong tac de chon run va so sanh `Early vs Late`.\r\n\r\n## Cach trinh bay\r\n- Chay paragraph setup truoc, sau do chay paragraph progress.\r\n- O dashboard, tap trung vao `Early avg return`, `Late avg return`, `Delta` va chart episode return.\r\n- Neu can giai thich them pipeline du lieu, quay lai paragraph setup va temp view Spark.\r\n","dateUpdated":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:41 AM","results":{"code":"SUCCESS","msg":[{"type":"HTML","data":"<div class=\"markdown-body\">\n<h1>Demo Learning Progress Cho PPO Trading</h1>\n<p>Notebook nay duoc doi huong de phuc vu demo voi thay: khong chi xem pipeline du lieu, ma con thay duoc thuat toan thay doi the nao tu luc moi hoc den luc hoc xong.</p>\n<h2>Flow de demo</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Paragraph setup dung <code>%pyspark</code> de load du lieu processed va tao temp view <code>trading_features_demo</code>.</li>\n<li>Paragraph progress doc artifact trong <code>results/runs</code> va tinh 2 giai doan cho tung run:<br />\n<code>Early</code> = trung binh cum episode dau, <code>Late</code> = trung binh cum episode cuoi.</li>\n<li>Paragraph <code>%angular</code> tao giao dien tuong tac de chon run va so sanh <code>Early vs Late</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Cach trinh bay</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Chay paragraph setup truoc, sau do chay paragraph progress.</li>\n<li>O dashboard, tap trung vao <code>Early avg return</code>, <code>Late avg return</code>, <code>Delta</code> va chart episode return.</li>\n<li>Neu can giai thich them pipeline du lieu, quay lai paragraph setup va temp view Spark.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>"}]},"dateStarted":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:41 AM","dateFinished":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:41 AM"},{"user":"sin235","progress":0,"config":{"lineNumbers":true,"editorSetting":{"language":"plain_text","editOnDblClick":false,"completionKey":"TAB","completionSupport":true},"editorMode":"ace/mode/plain_text","colWidth":12,"fontSize":9,"results":{},"enabled":true},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"apps":[],"runtimeInfos":{},"progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"jobName":"paragraph_1774070986497_1565894451","id":"paragraph_1774070986497_1565894451","dateCreated":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:29:46 AM","status":"ERROR","focus":false,"text":"%spark.pyspark\r\nimport json\r\nimport sys\r\n\r\nspark.sparkContext.setLogLevel('WARN')\r\n\r\nPROJECT_ROOT = 'D:/HCMUTE/RL/Project'\r\nif PROJECT_ROOT not in sys.path:\r\n    sys.path.insert(0, PROJECT_ROOT)\r\n\r\nfrom scripts.zeppelin_demo_helpers import bind_dashboard_payload, prepare_demo_dashboard\r\n\r\nsplit_dataset, demo_dashboard = prepare_demo_dashboard(\r\n    spark=spark,\r\n    project_root=PROJECT_ROOT,\r\n    sample_rows=12,\r\n    chart_rows=120,\r\n)\r\n\r\nsplit_dataset.createOrReplaceTempView('trading_features_demo')\r\nbind_dashboard_payload(z, demo_dashboard)\r\n\r\nprint(json.dumps(demo_dashboard['project'], indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\r\nprint('\\nTemp view created: trading_features_demo')\r\nprint('Angular binding created: demoDashboard')\r\n\r\nsplit_dataset.orderBy('symbol', 'time').show(15, truncate=False)\r\n","dateUpdated":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:41 AM","results":{"code":"ERROR","msg":[{"type":"TEXT","data":"\u001b[31m---------------------------------------------------------------------------\u001b[39m\n\u001b[31mModuleNotFoundError\u001b[39m                       Traceback (most recent call last)\n\u001b[36mCell\u001b[39m\u001b[36m \u001b[39m\u001b[32mIn[12]\u001b[39m\u001b[32m, line 10\u001b[39m\n\u001b[32m      7\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;28;01mif\u001b[39;00m PROJECT_ROOT \u001b[38;5;129;01mnot\u001b[39;00m \u001b[38;5;129;01min\u001b[39;00m sys.path:\n\u001b[32m      8\u001b[39m     sys.path.insert(\u001b[32m0\u001b[39m, PROJECT_ROOT)\n\u001b[32m---> \u001b[39m\u001b[32m10\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;28;01mfrom\u001b[39;00m\u001b[38;5;250m \u001b[39m\u001b[34;01mscripts\u001b[39;00m\u001b[34;01m.\u001b[39;00m\u001b[34;01mzeppelin_demo_helpers\u001b[39;00m\u001b[38;5;250m \u001b[39m\u001b[38;5;28;01mimport\u001b[39;00m bind_dashboard_payload, prepare_demo_dashboard\n\u001b[32m     12\u001b[39m split_dataset, demo_dashboard = prepare_demo_dashboard(\n\u001b[32m     13\u001b[39m     spark=spark,\n\u001b[32m     14\u001b[39m     project_root=PROJECT_ROOT,\n\u001b[32m     15\u001b[39m     sample_rows=\u001b[32m12\u001b[39m,\n\u001b[32m     16\u001b[39m     chart_rows=\u001b[32m120\u001b[39m,\n\u001b[32m     17\u001b[39m )\n\u001b[32m     19\u001b[39m split_dataset.createOrReplaceTempView(\u001b[33m'\u001b[39m\u001b[33mtrading_features_demo\u001b[39m\u001b[33m'\u001b[39m)\n\n\u001b[31mModuleNotFoundError\u001b[39m: No module named 'scripts'"}]},"dateStarted":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:41 AM","dateFinished":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:42 AM"},{"user":"sin235","progress":0,"config":{"editorMode":"ace/mode/plain_text","lineNumbers":true,"editorSetting":{"language":"plain_text","editOnDblClick":false,"completionKey":"TAB","completionSupport":true}},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"apps":[],"runtimeInfos":{},"progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"jobName":"paragraph_1774071464387_1618988555","id":"paragraph_1774071464387_1618988555","dateCreated":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:44 AM","status":"READY","focus":false,"text":"%spark.pyspark\r\nimport json\r\nimport sys\r\nfrom pyspark.sql import functions as F\r\n\r\nPROJECT_ROOT = 'D:/HCMUTE/RL/Project'\r\nif PROJECT_ROOT not in sys.path:\r\n    sys.path.insert(0, PROJECT_ROOT)\r\n\r\nfrom scripts.zeppelin_progress_demo_helpers import bind_learning_progress_payload, build_learning_progress_payload\r\n\r\nlearning_progress = build_learning_progress_payload(\r\n    project_root=PROJECT_ROOT,\r\n    preview_rows=10,\r\n)\r\nbind_learning_progress_payload(z, learning_progress)\r\n\r\noverview_rows = []\r\nfor run in learning_progress['runs']:\r\n    final_sharpe = run['summary']['sharpe_ratio']\r\n    if final_sharpe is None and run['eval']['final_test']:\r\n        final_sharpe = run['eval']['final_test'].get('sharpe_ratio')\r\n\r\n    overview_rows.append({\r\n        'run_id': run['run_id'],\r\n        'episodes': run['total_episodes'],\r\n        'window_size': run['window_size'],\r\n        'early_avg_return_pct': run['early']['avg_return_pct'],\r\n        'late_avg_return_pct': run['late']['avg_return_pct'],\r\n        'delta_return_pct': run['delta_return_pct'],\r\n        'final_sharpe': final_sharpe,\r\n    })\r\n\r\noverview_df = spark.createDataFrame(overview_rows)\r\n(\r\n    overview_df.orderBy(F.desc('episodes'))\r\n    .show(truncate=False)\r\n)\r\n\r\nprint(json.dumps(\r\n    {\r\n        'defaultRunId': learning_progress['defaultRunId'],\r\n        'availableRuns': [run['run_id'] for run in learning_progress['runs']],\r\n    },\r\n    indent=2,\r\n    ensure_ascii=False,\r\n))\r\n","dateUpdated":"Mar 21, 2026, 5:37:44 AM","results":{}},{"user":"sin235","progress":0,"config":{"lineNumbers":true,"editorMode":"ace/mode/plain_text","editorSetting":{"language":"plain_text","editOnDblClick":false,"completionKey":"TAB","completionSupport":true}},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"apps":[],"runtimeInfos":{},"progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"jobName":"paragraph_1774070400000_100004","id":"paragraph_1774071482011_1637558878","dateCreated":"2026-03-21T05:23:00+0000","status":404,"focus":false,"text":"%angular\r\n<style>\r\n  .lp-shell {\r\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\r\n    color: #0f172a;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf7 0%, #f8fafc 100%);\r\n    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\r\n    border-radius: 20px;\r\n    padding: 22px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-hero {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    justify-content: space-between;\r\n    gap: 18px;\r\n    align-items: stretch;\r\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-hero-copy {\r\n    flex: 1;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-kicker {\r\n    color: #0f766e;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    text-transform: uppercase;\r\n    letter-spacing: 0.08em;\r\n    font-weight: 800;\r\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-hero h2 {\r\n    margin: 0 0 10px 0;\r\n    font-size: 30px;\r\n    line-height: 1.1;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-hero p {\r\n    margin: 0;\r\n    color: #475569;\r\n    line-height: 1.55;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-highlight {\r\n    min-width: 280px;\r\n    background: #0f172a;\r\n    color: #f8fafc;\r\n    border-radius: 16px;\r\n    padding: 16px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-highlight-label {\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    text-transform: uppercase;\r\n    letter-spacing: 0.08em;\r\n    opacity: 0.7;\r\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-highlight-value {\r\n    font-size: 26px;\r\n    font-weight: 800;\r\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-toolbar {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    justify-content: space-between;\r\n    align-items: end;\r\n    gap: 14px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-toolbar label {\r\n    display: block;\r\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\r\n    font-size: 13px;\r\n    color: #475569;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-toolbar select {\r\n    min-width: 280px;\r\n    padding: 10px 12px;\r\n    border-radius: 12px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;\r\n    background: white;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-chip-row {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\r\n    gap: 8px;\r\n    justify-content: flex-end;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-chip {\r\n    background: #fef3c7;\r\n    color: #92400e;\r\n    border-radius: 999px;\r\n    padding: 6px 10px;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    font-weight: 700;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-kpi-grid,\r\n  .lp-mini-grid {\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));\r\n    gap: 12px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-card {\r\n    background: white;\r\n    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\r\n    border-radius: 16px;\r\n    padding: 14px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-card-label {\r\n    color: #64748b;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    text-transform: uppercase;\r\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-card-value {\r\n    font-size: 26px;\r\n    font-weight: 800;\r\n    color: #0f172a;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-card-sub {\r\n    margin-top: 6px;\r\n    color: #475569;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-positive {\r\n    color: #15803d;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-negative {\r\n    color: #b91c1c;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-layout {\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1.7fr 1fr;\r\n    gap: 16px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-panel {\r\n    background: white;\r\n    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\r\n    border-radius: 16px;\r\n    padding: 16px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-panel h3 {\r\n    margin: 0 0 8px 0;\r\n    font-size: 18px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-panel p {\r\n    margin: 0 0 12px 0;\r\n    color: #475569;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-chart-meta {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\r\n    gap: 8px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-chart-meta span {\r\n    background: #ecfeff;\r\n    color: #155e75;\r\n    border-radius: 999px;\r\n    padding: 6px 10px;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    font-weight: 700;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-chart-box {\r\n    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fcfffd 0%, #eff6ff 100%);\r\n    border-radius: 14px;\r\n    padding: 8px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-chart-box svg {\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    height: 250px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-table {\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    border-collapse: collapse;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-table th,\r\n  .lp-table td {\r\n    padding: 9px 8px;\r\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\r\n    text-align: left;\r\n    font-size: 13px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-table th {\r\n    color: #475569;\r\n    font-weight: 700;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-stage-grid {\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n    gap: 16px;\r\n  }\r\n  .lp-note {\r\n    margin-top: 10px;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    color: #64748b;\r\n  }\r\n  @media (max-width: 980px) {\r\n    .lp-hero,\r\n    .lp-toolbar,\r\n    .lp-layout,\r\n    .lp-stage-grid {\r\n      display: block;\r\n    }\r\n    .lp-highlight,\r\n    .lp-panel {\r\n      margin-top: 14px;\r\n    }\r\n    .lp-kpi-grid,\r\n    .lp-mini-grid {\r\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class='lp-shell' ng-if='learningProgressDashboard.runs' ng-init='selectedRunId = learningProgressDashboard.defaultRunId'>\r\n  <div ng-repeat='current in [learningProgressDashboard.runMap[selectedRunId]]'>\r\n    <div class='lp-hero'>\r\n      <div class='lp-hero-copy'>\r\n        <div class='lp-kicker'>Learning Progress Demo</div>\r\n        <h2>PPO hoc it ra sao, hoc xong ra sao</h2>\r\n        <p>\r\n          Dashboard nay tap trung vao artifact training da co san trong `results/runs`.\r\n          `Early` la trung binh cua cum episode dau, `Late` la trung binh cua cum episode cuoi cua run dang chon.\r\n          Muc tieu la de thay nhin thay duoc xu huong cai thien ngay trong notebook.\r\n        </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-highlight'>\r\n        <div class='lp-highlight-label'>Run dang xem</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-highlight-value'>{{current.run_id}}</div>\r\n        <div>{{current.total_episodes}} episodes | window {{current.window_size}} episodes</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class='lp-toolbar'>\r\n      <div>\r\n        <label>Chon run de demo</label>\r\n        <select ng-model='selectedRunId' ng-options='run.run_id as run.label for run in learningProgressDashboard.runs'></select>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-chip-row'>\r\n        <span class='lp-chip'>Early: {{current.early.label}}</span>\r\n        <span class='lp-chip'>Late: {{current.late.label}}</span>\r\n        <span class='lp-chip'>Updates: {{current.total_updates}}</span>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class='lp-kpi-grid'>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Early Avg Return</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{current.early.avg_return_pct | number:2}}%</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Trung binh cum episode dau</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Late Avg Return</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{current.late.avg_return_pct | number:2}}%</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Trung binh cum episode cuoi</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Delta</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value' ng-class='current.delta_return_pct >= 0 ? \"lp-positive\" : \"lp-negative\"'>{{current.delta_return_pct | number:2}} pts</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Late - Early</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Total Episodes</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{current.total_episodes}}</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>So episode co log</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class='lp-mini-grid'>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Best Episode</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{current.best_episode.total_return_pct | number:2}}%</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Episode {{current.best_episode.episode}}</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Worst Episode</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{current.worst_episode.total_return_pct | number:2}}%</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Episode {{current.worst_episode.episode}}</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Final Sharpe</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{(current.summary.sharpe_ratio != null ? current.summary.sharpe_ratio : current.eval.final_test.sharpe_ratio) | number:3}}</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Lay tu summary neu co, neu khong lay test eval</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class='lp-card'>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-label'>Final Total Return</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-value'>{{((current.summary.total_return != null ? current.summary.total_return : current.eval.final_test.total_return) * 100) | number:2}}%</div>\r\n        <div class='lp-card-sub'>Tong return cuoi run</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class='lp-layout'>\r\n      <div class='lp-panel'>\r\n        <h3>Episode Return Curve</h3>\r\n        <p>Duong xam la return cua tung episode, duong xanh la moving average de thay xu huong hoc.</p>\r\n        <div class='lp-chart-meta'>\r\n          <span>Min {{current.chart.min_value | number:2}}%</span>\r\n          <span>Max {{current.chart.max_value | number:2}}%</span>\r\n          <span>Latest {{current.chart.latest_value | number:2}}%</span>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class='lp-chart-box'>\r\n          <svg viewBox='0 0 620 220' preserveAspectRatio='none'>\r\n            <line ng-if='current.chart.zero_y != null' x1='14' x2='606' ng-attr-y1='{{current.chart.zero_y}}' ng-attr-y2='{{current.chart.zero_y}}' stroke='#cbd5e1' stroke-dasharray='6 6'></line>\r\n            <polyline ng-attr-points='{{current.chart.raw_points}}' fill='none' stroke='#94a3b8' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'></polyline>\r\n            <polyline ng-attr-points='{{current.chart.ma_points}}' fill='none' stroke='#0f766e' stroke-width='4' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'></polyline>\r\n          </svg>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class='lp-note'>Neu duong moving average ve sau cao hon ve dau, thay co the noi rang agent dang hoc de dat ket qua tot hon o giai doan cuoi.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class='lp-panel'>\r\n        <h3>Run Snapshot</h3>\r\n        <table class='lp-table'>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr><th>Total timesteps</th><td>{{current.config.total_timesteps}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><th>n_steps</th><td>{{current.config.n_steps}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><th>batch_size</th><td>{{current.config.batch_size}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><th>hidden_size</th><td>{{current.config.hidden_size}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><th>max_steps_train</th><td>{{current.config.max_steps_train}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><th>max_steps_eval</th><td>{{current.config.max_steps_eval}}</td></tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n\r\n        <h3 style='margin-top: 16px;'>Eval Snapshot</h3>\r\n        <table class='lp-table'>\r\n          <thead>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <th>Stage</th>\r\n              <th>Episode</th>\r\n              <th>Sharpe</th>\r\n              <th>Return</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </thead>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <td>First val</td>\r\n              <td>{{current.eval.first_val.episode}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{current.eval.first_val.sharpe_ratio | number:3}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{(current.eval.first_val.total_return * 100) | number:2}}%</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <td>Last val</td>\r\n              <td>{{current.eval.last_val.episode}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{current.eval.last_val.sharpe_ratio | number:3}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{(current.eval.last_val.total_return * 100) | number:2}}%</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <td>Final test</td>\r\n              <td>{{current.eval.final_test.episode}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{current.eval.final_test.sharpe_ratio | number:3}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{(current.eval.final_test.total_return * 100) | number:2}}%</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n\r\n        <h3 style='margin-top: 16px;' ng-if='current.split.train'>Data Split</h3>\r\n        <table class='lp-table' ng-if='current.split.train'>\r\n          <thead>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <th>Split</th>\r\n              <th>Start</th>\r\n              <th>End</th>\r\n              <th>Days</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </thead>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr><td>train</td><td>{{current.split.train.start}}</td><td>{{current.split.train.end}}</td><td>{{current.split.train.days}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><td>val</td><td>{{current.split.val.start}}</td><td>{{current.split.val.end}}</td><td>{{current.split.val.days}}</td></tr>\r\n            <tr><td>test</td><td>{{current.split.test.start}}</td><td>{{current.split.test.end}}</td><td>{{current.split.test.days}}</td></tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class='lp-stage-grid'>\r\n      <div class='lp-panel'>\r\n        <h3>{{current.early.label}}</h3>\r\n        <p>Bang nay giup thay nhin ro cum episode luc agent moi bat dau hoc.</p>\r\n        <table class='lp-table'>\r\n          <thead>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <th>Episode</th>\r\n              <th>Return</th>\r\n              <th>Portfolio</th>\r\n              <th>Trades</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </thead>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr ng-repeat='row in current.early.rows'>\r\n              <td>{{row.episode}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{row.total_return_pct | number:2}}%</td>\r\n              <td>{{row.portfolio_value | number:0}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{row.n_trades}}</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class='lp-panel'>\r\n        <h3>{{current.late.label}}</h3>\r\n        <p>Bang nay la cum episode cuoi de doi chieu voi giai doan dau.</p>\r\n        <table class='lp-table'>\r\n          <thead>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <th>Episode</th>\r\n              <th>Return</th>\r\n              <th>Portfolio</th>\r\n              <th>Trades</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </thead>\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr ng-repeat='row in current.late.rows'>\r\n              <td>{{row.episode}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{row.total_return_pct | number:2}}%</td>\r\n              <td>{{row.portfolio_value | number:0}}</td>\r\n              <td>{{row.n_trades}}</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n          </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n","dateUpdated":"2026-03-21T05:23:00+0000","results":{}},{"user":"sin235","progress":0,"config":{"colWidth":12,"fontSize":9,"results":{},"enabled":true,"editorSetting":{"language":"plain_text"}},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"apps":[],"runtimeInfos":{},"progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"jobName":"paragraph_1774070400000_100005","id":"paragraph_1774070400000_100005","dateCreated":"2026-03-21T05:24:00+0000","status":"READY","focus":false,"text":"%md\n## Cach demo voi thay\n1. Chon run o dashboard.\n2. Chi vao `Early avg return`, `Late avg return` va `Delta` de mo ta agent cai thien theo qua trinh hoc.\n3. Dung chart episode return de giai thich xu huong hoc, sau do cuon xuong bang `Early` va `Late` de so doi mat tung episode.\n4. Neu thay hoi du lieu vao tu dau, quay lai paragraph setup va temp view `trading_features_demo`.\n","dateUpdated":"2026-03-21T05:24:00+0000","results":{}}],"info":{},"noteForms":{},"noteParams":{},"angularObjects":{}}